project_descr: The project aims to contribute to the maintenance of peace and stability that has been achieved so far in the Bangsamoro, and to support the strengthening of enabling conditions for the continuation of the peace process beyond the Aquino administration.

outputs.output_descr: The project aims to contribute to the maintenance of peace and stability that has been achieved so far in the Bangsamoro, and to support the strengthening of enabling conditions for the continuation of the peace process beyond the Aquino administration.
This Project will contribute to efforts to strengthen the enabling environment for peace and stability and sustain the gains for peace and development in the Bangsamoro.

document_name: Supporting an Enabling Environment for Sustainable Peace in the Bangsamoro
Peace and Reconciliation Initiatives for Empowerment in the Bangsamoro
